jltl2dstar

Class DAUnionAlgorithm

  • java.lang.Object
    • jltl2dstar.DAUnionAlgorithm

  • public class DAUnionAlgorithm
extends java.lang.Object
    An algorithm calculating the union of two DA. Requires the existance of a UnionAcceptanceCalculator for the AcceptanceCondition.
